{"tid":644590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強行拉開月台幕門欲衝上車 滬女被困動彈不得","createTime":"2018-04-27T10:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T13:58:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"176fbe9c5b10afd06370254da2f5fac4f88984d0","tid":644590,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180427/_2018042715155956604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180427%2F_2018042715155956604.jpg&h=50491378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日內地社交網站流傳一段影片，片中一名女子被夾在地鐵閘門與月台幕門之間，高速行駛的列車更不時摩擦到女子手中的物品，嚇得她只能緊緊貼着幕門站。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，事件在上海寶安公路地鐵站發生，有目擊事件的網民表示，該名女子在車門快關上時，邊喊前快遲到，邊用手強行拉開月台幕門登上地鐵，豈料下一秒車門就關上，女子便被夾在中間，動彈不得。而地鐵工作人員則表示，已接到乘客的反映，相關部門正在調查，結果需等待一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n有地鐵工作人員表示，列車車門和月台幕門雖裝有防夾裝置，但當有人被夾在車門和幕門之間，防夾裝置是無法感應到。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民看過影片很都不同情該女子的遭遇，「腦子進水了」、「自己作得死最好不要讓別人來救她」 、「真正叫『不作死就不會死』，非要作死自己，那再完善的保障都抵擋不了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面有片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1201935/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1201935%2F&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65liS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=da9e8986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1201935%2F&h=6bf48747\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1201935/</a><br />\n<br />\n再企前少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65906cf9bd96466bbfe884b63be75775ea42902","tid":644590,"uid":45696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ee0c99d69a305e16f323cc55e4e2e8b424abbc","tid":644590,"uid":176366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,